{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回\"法场\"讲述秘密处决丁宁前的多方布局。韦好客在刑部大膳房后的秘密煤场设立法场，重金聘请一位神秘监斩官防范意外。监斩官到场后发现法场戒备森严，认为自己多余准备离去，韦好客以两个女人为由挽留：一是他昔日身边的小景已成江湖名女人花景因梦，她送来丁宁却不想让他死得太快，很可能制造意外；二是慕容秋水身边的柳伴伴，已从慕容处取得杀手资料和珠宝，招揽了可怕的杀手。与此同时，柳伴伴被变态侏儒牧羊儿控制，牧羊儿带她前往法场观看丁宁处决。牧羊儿通过煤场管事詹天福的秘道进入法场，以五百两金叶子和柳伴伴为代价达成交易。本章揭示花景因梦与监斩官的师徒过往，以及法场背后的多方势力角力。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "谢天谢地，你总算及时赶来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "除了你以外，有没有别人知道我会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "没有。绝对没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "执刑的是姜断弦，姜断弦就是彭十三豆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "是。我已经亲自监督清查过三次，场上的卫卒也都是我亲手训练出来的，绝不会有什么问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "犯人呢？听说他本来也是个厉害的角色。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "不但厉害，而且很厉害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你是用什么绑住他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "如果连你都扯不断这条绳子，世上还有谁能挣得脱？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你说得对。再见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "再见？再见是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "再见的意思就是说我要走了。现在我还可以再说一遍！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "不行，你不能对我说再见。别人都可以说，你不能说。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "因为你还有十五万七千五百两银子没有拿走。你答应要为我做此事也没有做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "这件事，我是不会做的了。所以银子我也不能要。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "其实你不问也应该知道的，多年以前，你已经很了解我这个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我要你十五万七千五百两银子，你肯给我，当然是因为我值得，我当然也受之无愧。因为那时候我一直认为这件事非要我来做不可！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "事情本来就是这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "可是现在情况不同了，所以我连你一文钱都不能收。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "现在的情况为什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你用高价请我来，只为了要我防止法场上所有的意外，让姜断弦可以顺利执行。我肯来，只因为我觉得你既然肯出如此高价，被处决的当然是一名极重要的人物，会发生意外的可能极大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "可是现在我才知道这件事根本用不着我来做的。因为法场上根本就不可能会有任何意外发生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你不但把这件事做得非常机密，而且把每一个细节都安排得很好，连我都找不出一点疏忽，何况还有你和姜断弦这样的绝顶高手在场监督，就算有什么意外，有你们两位在也已足够。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "所以这次你请我来根本就是多余的，所以我才只有对你说再见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "你还是不能走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "因为两个人。两个女人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "女人？一件事如果牵涉到女人，就比较麻烦了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "这种事怎么会牵涉到女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "这一点你不问也应该知道的。这个世界上又有哪一件事没有牵涉到女人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "尤其是这件事，根本就是一个女人引起来的。这个女人跟你好像也有点关系！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你说的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "十年之前，你身边是不是总带着一个姓景的小女孩？我记得你好像还把你独门传授的一套分筋错骨手教给了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你说的是小景？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "不错，我说的就是她。只不过这位小景姑娘早就已经长大了，而且已经变成了江湖中最有名的一位名女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我知道。我知道那位了不起的因梦夫人就是景因梦。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "不是景因梦，是花景因梦。你既然知道她跟你离开之后的那一段辉煌事迹，当然也应该知道她已经嫁给了江湖中最有名的浪子花错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "今天要处决的犯人，就是花景因梦送来的，可是她又不想要他死得太快，所以今天她很可能要到这里制造一些意外，她会做出些什么事，会请到些什么人来，我一点都猜不到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "所以我就问我自己，这个世界上如果还有一个人能猜透花景因梦的做法，这个人是谁呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "这个人当然就是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "另外一个女人，就是你绝不会认得的了。十年前你还在江湖中行走时，她还是个刚断奶的孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "这个孩子现在是不是也已经长大？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "不但长大了，而且长得非常好看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "有多好看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "我也说不出她究竟有多好看，我只知道连慕容公子都迷上了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "能够把慕容秋水迷住的女人，总是有点道理的。像这样的女人，随时都可以制造出一些让人头痛的意外来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你说的这个女人，是不是柳伴伴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "我真是想不到，这几年来，你好像已经不太过问江湖的事了。想不到你对我们的事还是知道这么多。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "如果你们随时都能找到我，我怎么能不知道你们的事……一个人想要好好的活下去，就不能不知道一些他根本不想知道的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "只可惜有一些他很想知道的事，他却总是不知道。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "柳伴伴的人虽然已经长大了，做出来的事却还是常常会像一个小孩子，所以她并不可怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "可怕的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "可怕的是那些她一定会去找，而且一定能找到的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "一个小女孩竟然能找到能让你觉得可怕的人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "因为她看到了姜断弦档案中最可怕的几位杀手的资料。而且她也有本事从慕容那里拿走了一批足够打动那些杀手的珠宝。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "那些珠宝和那些资料，是不是慕容秋水故意让她拿走的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "慕容为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "因为这件事，一定有阴谋，所以你们一定要制造一些混乱，让别人摸不透这件事究竟是怎么回事。如果事情不是这样子的，那么一个小姑娘怎么能在慕容眼前玩花样？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "如果不是慕容故意放手，这位柳伴伴姑娘恐怕连他的一只袜子都拿不走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "这件事究竟是怎么回事，我也不知道。我只知道这件事的确是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "所以你也一定要相信，柳伴伴一定已经用那批珠宝请到了我们资料中记录的一些最可怕的杀手。而且最近我们根本看不到她的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "监斩官",
      "listener": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "text": "你认为她能找来的是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_hao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "韦好客",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhan_guan",
      "text": "我不知道。就因为我不知道，所以我才肯花十五万七千五百两银子请你来，所以你也就绝不能对我说再见了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "你不给我吃的，我就挨饿，你不给我穿的，我就挨冻，我吃的穿的连一只麻雀都比不上，我都忍住了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "可是我实在不明白，现在你为什么连觉都不让我睡了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "因为今天是个特别的日子。今天我要带你去看一样特别的东西。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "去看一个人的脑袋怎么样离开他的脖子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "这件事一定有趣得很，每一个动作我都不会错过的。我相信你一定也不肯错过的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "你说的这个人是丁宁？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "大概是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "今天已经是三月十五日？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "好，我跟你去。你能不能找一件完整的衣裳给我穿？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "求求你，现在我已经是你的女人了，你总不能让我光着身子走出去吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "我不是不让你穿衣服，而是你根本就不必穿衣服。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "因为这一路上根本就不会有人看见你。这当然是个秘密，我只能告诉你一个人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "今天的法场，和平常完全不同，根本就禁止旁观，无论谁只要妄入一步，一律格杀勿论。幸好我还是有法子可以进去，你应该知道无论遇到什么事，我都有法子对付。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "连你这样的女人我都能对付，还有什么事是我对付不了的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "人来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "什么人来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "当然是带路的人，这个老乌龟虽然不能算是个人，却只有他可以带我们进法场。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "这个老八旦姓詹，是个烧煤的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "speaker_name": "柳伴伴",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "一个烧煤的老头能带我们进法场？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_liu_ban_ban",
      "text": "你很快就会明白的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "韦好客就算再不争气，也不会在这里杀人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "这里本来就不是杀人的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "那你为什么带我来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我只说这里不是杀人的地方，可没说这里不是收钱的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经可以带我去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "还不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我的年纪大了，眼睛也不行了，刚才也不知道是不是看见了鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "你看见的是个什么样的鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "好像是个女鬼，一条腿好长好长的，身上好像连衣服都没有穿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "你看见那个女鬼身上长着的真是一条腿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "当然不是一条腿，是一双腿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "如果一双腿，那么你看见的就不是女鬼了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "可是在这么冷的天气里，她身上只挂着点破布，为什么好像一点都不冷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "因为她不怕冷。她从小就是在高山上长大的，从小就光着屁股满山乱跑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "那么我刚刚看的真是一个女人？不是女鬼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "你放心，错不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "如果我们车子上真有那么样一个女人，你就错了，而且错得厉害。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "我有什么错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "我们当初说好的，我带你们进法场，一个人五百两金叶子。你为什么要带一个女人来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "我不该带女人来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "当然不该。你应该知道，你也不是不知道，女人的嘴巴有多大，万一把我的秘密泄漏出去怎么办？你是不是要把我这个脑袋瓜子砍了去喂狗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "我绝没有这个意思！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "那么你就应该知道，在做我们这种事情的时候，女人根本就不能算人，如果你一定要带着她，我们这次的交易就算吹了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "text": "果然姜是老的辣，果然想得周到，其实我的想法也跟你老人家一样，有时候女人根本就不是人。其实我对这件事情也早就有了打算。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
      "speaker_name": "老詹",
      "listener": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "text": "什么打算？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_yang_er",
      "speaker_name": "牧羊儿",
      "listener": "char_zhan_tian_fu",
